{"tid":1865762,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"李兆基超越李嘉誠成福布斯香港首富","createTime":"2020-02-06T10:57:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-08T19:36:40.000Z","uid":1086,"like":6,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"e4620cf0c51a0905329f517e07706c4e986c12c0","tid":1865762,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T10:57:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://plib.aastocks.com/aafnnews/image/medialib/20180315134207237_m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fplib.aastocks.com%2Faafnnews%2Fimage%2Fmedialib%2F20180315134207237_m.jpg&h=a877c482&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n福布斯公布2020年香港富豪榜，恒地創辦人及前主席李兆基以<span style=\"color: red;\">304億美元</span>(約2,360億港元)身家，超越長和系資深顧問李嘉誠成為香港首富。連續多年為香港首富的李嘉誠<span style=\"color: red;\">以294億美元</span>(約2,282億港元)退居排名榜次位，新世界及周大福 主席鄭家純以<span style=\"color: red;\">207億美元</span>(約1,607億港元)排名第三。<br />\n<br />\n另外，華人置業大股東劉鑾雄及銀娛主席呂志和分別以169億美元及154億美元身家排第四及第五，第6至10位依次為李錦記李文達、郭老太鄺肖卿、吳光正、蔡崇信及楊建文和林惠英夫婦。"},{"pid":"9a074d321c51d30065a9dbe0cb6b75d72f5acca4","tid":1865762,"uid":59047,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T10:58:45.000Z","msg":"誠哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e59c78bd369f224fb6d76baadcd6d7852df9dacc","tid":1865762,"uid":60488,"like":25,"dislike":2,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T11:01:21.000Z","msg":"誠個派錢都派左1億美金啦"},{"pid":"133eecdeaaea7f9dd839b43fee1516486c77005c","tid":1865762,"uid":177326,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T11:03:30.000Z","msg":"之前有人超越誠哥唔駛幾耐已經無好日子過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23e978183d816b3a94fdd46a4d126d7b2585ae69","tid":1865762,"uid":108756,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T11:03:52.000Z","msg":"差個十億美金姐"},{"pid":"4b58780781e2a90d43c34fb956ed0dbb77ee6f06","tid":1865762,